newCmd('',' ','','*v+11.0;','In situations where there are multiple models, typically only one model is displayed at any given time. In that situation, if a user clicks on a pair of atoms to measure a bond distance, then only one measurement is made. Using <b>set measureAllModels ON</b>, when the user makes measurements in any one frame, ALL similar measurements in all models in hidden frames are generated at the same time. <b>set measureAllModels ON</b> thus allows for very efficient measuring and investigation of differences in a bond distance or bond angle or dihedral angle across multiple models.  ','*500','measureAllModels','OFF')
