newCmd('','11.9.23','','*v+12.0;','Generates a relatively compact JVXL XML "vertex-only" mesh surface file from an isosurface. A typical command, after creation of an isosurface, would be <b>write MESH t.jvxl</b>. Note that standard JVXL files are considerably smaller, however.','*2','MESH','&quot;fileName&quot;')
