newCmd('.zoomto',' ','','*v+11.0 -- new;anim;nav','Carries out a smooth transition to the specified zoom setting. Indicating a new rotation center is optional. All capabilities of {#.zoom~} are supported. Jmol 13.0 adds centering on isosurfaces using $xxx.','1|0','','')
newCmd('',' ','','*v+11.0;','By itself, <b>zoomTo</b> smoothly zooms IN by a factor of 2 over the course of 1 second.','*1','','')
