newCmd('','','','*v+11.0;','Smoothly moves the specified atom or coordinate to the center of the window if windowCentered or designates it as the center of rotation if not windowCentered. xTrans and yTrans parameters specify percent translation within the window along X and Y, respectively (Jmol 12.0). All parameters are options. The default time is 1 second; indicating no center position results in simple, smooth zooming.','*3','._floattime','{{atom expression}} or {{x y z}} or $xxx')
