newCmd('','','','*v+11.0;','Multiplies or divides the current zoom setting by the indicated factor over the course of the specified number of seconds. Optional xTrans and yTrans parameters specify percent translation within the window along X and Y, respectively (Jmol 12.0)','*6','._floattime','{{atom expression}} or {{x y z}} or $xxx',' * or / factor','xTrans yTrans')
